====== Concat Table Plugin for DokuWiki ======

 * Gets tables from other pages, combines them and outputs the result
 * Can also be used to include and reformat a single table

Usage:
	{{concat>page1#section|page2#section|...|pageX#section}}
	{{concat>page1#section|page2#section|...|pageX#section&flag1&flag2&...&flagX}}
	{{concat>page1#section&flag1&flag2&...&flagX}}
	
Available Flags:
	code			formats the table in a way that makes sense for documenting code
	noheadings		removes all table headings from the entire table



